    <entry>
      <title>Auto Setting in Typora makes pictures missing in Pages</title>
      <link href="/2021/06/30/Auto-Setting-in-Typora-makes-pictures-missing-in-Pages/"/>
      <url>/2021/06/30/Auto-Setting-in-Typora-makes-pictures-missing-in-Pages/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Demo-1-Insert-from-local-drive-with-relative-path"><a href="#Demo-1-Insert-from-local-drive-with-relative-path" class="headerlink" title="Demo 1 -Insert from local drive with relative path"></a>Demo 1 -Insert from local drive with relative path</h2><p><code>&#123;% gallery %&#125; ![](src) &#123;% endgallery %&#125;</code></p><div class="justified-gallery"><p><img src="D:\csite\source\_posts\Auto-Setting-in-Typora-makes-pictures-missing-in-Pages\IMG_20160529_181142-1625121524217.jpg" alt=""></p><p><img src="D:\csite\source\_posts\Auto-Setting-in-Typora-makes-pictures-missing-in-Pages\IMG_20160530_203034-1625121524217.jpg" alt="IMG_20160530_203034"></p><p><img src="D:\csite\source\_posts\Auto-Setting-in-Typora-makes-pictures-missing-in-Pages\IMG_20160531_133425-1625121524221.jpg" alt="IMG_20160531_133425"></p>          </div><p>Conclusion: Pictures work well in Typora, but are all missing in Page. </p><h2 id="Demo-2-Insert-from-local-drive-with-relative-path"><a href="#Demo-2-Insert-from-local-drive-with-relative-path" class="headerlink" title="Demo 2 -Insert from local drive with relative path"></a>Demo 2 -Insert from local drive with relative path</h2><p><code>![](src)</code></p><p><img src="D:\csite\source\_posts\Auto-Setting-in-Typora-makes-pictures-missing-in-Pages\IMG_20160529_205147-1625180574851.jpg" alt=""></p><p><img src="D:\csite\source\_posts\Auto-Setting-in-Typora-makes-pictures-missing-in-Pages\IMG_20160529_194901-1625180607241.jpg" alt=""></p><p>Conclusion: Pictures work well in Typora, but are all missing in Page. <code>Markdown Image Path does not exists!</code></p><h2 id="Demo-3-Upload-to-external-link-and-use-src-external-link"><a href="#Demo-3-Upload-to-external-link-and-use-src-external-link" class="headerlink" title="Demo 3 -Upload to external link and use src=external link"></a>Demo 3 -Upload to external link and use src=external link</h2><p><code>&#123;% gallery %&#125; ![](external link) &#123;% endgallery %&#125;</code></p><p>uncheck “allow to prioritize the use of relative path”! When copying external ink, the src becomes absolute path. No good. I need the link remains a link! Setting in Typora.</p><p>uncheck “apply the rules to link based pictures”!</p><div class="justified-gallery"><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/07/01/mGh8iuqKTAc93Dr.jpg" alt=""></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/07/01/jQO9JSbtUzmTqL5.jpg" alt=""></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/07/01/mAtZsVUPSXeMgNx.jpg" alt=""></p>          </div><h2 id="Demo-4-Upload-to-external-link-and-use-src-external-link"><a href="#Demo-4-Upload-to-external-link-and-use-src-external-link" class="headerlink" title="Demo 4 -Upload to external link and use src=external link"></a>Demo 4 -Upload to external link and use src=external link</h2><p><code>![](external link)</code></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/07/01/mAtZsVUPSXeMgNx.jpg" alt=""></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/07/01/jQO9JSbtUzmTqL5.jpg" alt=""></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/07/01/mGh8iuqKTAc93Dr.jpg" alt=""></p><p>Now Demo 3 and Demo 4 work properly, each in the way it being designed to be. </p><h2 id="Lesson-Learned"><a href="#Lesson-Learned" class="headerlink" title="Lesson Learned"></a>Lesson Learned</h2><h3 id="Work-Flow-of-Editing-pictures-in-a-Post"><a href="#Work-Flow-of-Editing-pictures-in-a-Post" class="headerlink" title="Work Flow of Editing pictures in a Post"></a>Work Flow of Editing pictures in a Post</h3><p>This setting in Typora may work properly:</p><h3 id="Work-Flow-of-Editing-pictures-in-a-Page"><a href="#Work-Flow-of-Editing-pictures-in-a-Page" class="headerlink" title="Work Flow of Editing pictures in a Page"></a>Work Flow of Editing pictures in a Page</h3><ol><li>Upload the images to external links</li><li>Adjust the setting in Typora by uncheck of two boxes</li><li>Copy external link to <code>![](external link)</code></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>How to use icons from Font Awesome 5.x in your website?</title>
      <link href="/2021/06/30/How-to-use-Font-Awesome-in-your-website/"/>
      <url>/2021/06/30/How-to-use-Font-Awesome-in-your-website/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Referencing-Icons"><a href="#Referencing-Icons" class="headerlink" title="Referencing Icons"></a>Referencing Icons</h2><p>First of all, I suspect that the version of embedded Font Awesome to be 5, because New in Font Awesome 5 is the <strong>fas prefix</strong> or <strong>fab prefix</strong>, while Font Awesome 4 uses <strong>fa</strong>. Now let’s see which icons are already available from Font Awesome 5.x as embedded into the Butterfly theme. </p><h3 id="By-fas-prefix"><a href="#By-fas-prefix" class="headerlink" title="By fas prefix"></a>By <code>fas</code> prefix</h3><p>Use examples are as follows:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-user&quot;&gt; fa-user&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-video&quot;&gt; fa-video&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-folder&quot;&gt; fa-folder&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-image&quot;&gt; fa-image&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-heart&quot;&gt; fa-heart&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-bars&quot;&gt; fa-bars&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>This is how they look like:<br><i class="fas fa-user"> fa-user</i><br><i class="fas fa-video"> fa-video</i><br><i class="fas fa-folder"> fa-folder</i><br><i class="fas fa-image"> fa-image</i><br><i class="fas fa-heart"> fa-heart</i><br><i class="fas fa-bars"> fa-bars</i></p><h3 id="By-fab-prefix"><a href="#By-fab-prefix" class="headerlink" title="By fab prefix"></a>By <code>fab</code> prefix</h3><p>Use examples are as follows:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-android&quot;&gt; fa-android&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-apple&quot;&gt; fa-apple&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-bluetooth&quot;&gt; fa-bluetooth&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-bluetooth-b&quot;&gt; fa-bluetooth-b&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-alipay&quot;&gt; fa-alipay&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-qq&quot;&gt; fa-qq&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>This is how they look like:<br><i class="fab fa-android"> fa-android</i><br><i class="fab fa-apple"> fa-apple</i><br><i class="fab fa-bluetooth"> fa-bluetooth</i><br><i class="fab fa-bluetooth-b"> fa-bluetooth-b</i><br><i class="fab fa-alipay"> fa-alipay</i><br><i class="fab fa-qq"> fa-qq</i></p><h3 id="The-Icon-Cheatsheet"><a href="#The-Icon-Cheatsheet" class="headerlink" title="The Icon Cheatsheet"></a>The Icon Cheatsheet</h3><p>Here is an exhaustive list of all icons that are available from Font Awesome 5.x, and you will need to search first before you could pick the desired proper ones for free adoption into your own project. </p><p><a href="https://www.fontawesomecheatsheet.com/font-awesome-cheatsheet-5x/">Font Awesome Cheatsheet v5.x</a></p><h2 id="Icons-for-Audio-Video"><a href="#Icons-for-Audio-Video" class="headerlink" title="Icons for Audio / Video"></a>Icons for Audio / Video</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-power-off&quot;&gt; fa-power-off&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-play&quot;&gt; fa-play&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-play-circle&quot;&gt;fa-play-circle&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-pause&quot;&gt; fa-pause&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-pause-circle&quot;&gt; fa-pause-circle&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-stop&quot;&gt; fa-stop&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-stop-circle&quot;&gt; fa-stop-circle&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-step-backward&quot;&gt; fa-step-backward&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-step-forward&quot;&gt; fa-step-forward&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-fast-backward&quot;&gt; fa-fast-backward&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-fast-forward&quot;&gt; fa-fast-forward&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-signal&quot;&gt; fa-signal&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-bluetooth&quot;&gt; fa-bluetooth&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-bluetooth-b&quot;&gt; fa-bluetooth-b&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-bell&quot;&gt; fa-bell&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-bell-slash&quot;&gt; fa-bell-slash&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-headphones&quot;&gt; fa-headphones&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-headphones-alt&quot;&gt; fa-headphones-alt&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-headset&quot;&gt; fa-headset&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-microphone&quot;&gt; fa-microphone&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-microphone-slash&quot;&gt; fa-microphone-slash&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-microphone-alt&quot;&gt; fa-microphone-alt&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-microphone-alt-slash&quot;&gt; fa-microphone-alt-slash&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-music&quot;&gt; fa-music&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-volume-down&quot;&gt; fa-volume-down&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-volume-up&quot;&gt; fa-volume-up&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-volume-off&quot;&gt; fa-volume-off&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-volume-mute&quot;&gt; fa-volume-mute&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><i class="fas fa-power-off"> fa-power-off</i><br><i class="fas fa-play"> fa-play</i>     <i class="fas fa-play-circle">fa-play-circle</i><br><i class="fas fa-pause"> fa-pause</i>     <i class="fas fa-pause-circle"> fa-pause-circle</i><br><i class="fas fa-stop"> fa-stop</i>     <i class="fas fa-stop-circle"> fa-stop-circle</i><br><i class="fas fa-step-backward"> fa-step-backward</i>     <i class="fas fa-step-forward"> fa-step-forward</i><br><i class="fas fa-fast-backward"> fa-fast-backward</i>     <i class="fas fa-fast-forward"> fa-fast-forward</i><br><i class="fas fa-signal"> fa-signal</i><br><i class="fab fa-bluetooth"> fa-bluetooth</i>     <i class="fab fa-bluetooth-b"> fa-bluetooth-b</i><br><i class="fas fa-bell"> fa-bell</i>     <i class="fas fa-bell-slash"> fa-bell-slash</i><br><i class="fas fa-headphones"> fa-headphones</i>     <i class="fas fa-headphones-alt"> fa-headphones-alt</i>     <i class="fas fa-headset"> fa-headset</i><br><i class="fas fa-microphone"> fa-microphone</i>     <i class="fas fa-microphone-slash"> fa-microphone-slash</i><br><i class="fas fa-microphone-alt"> fa-microphone-alt</i>     <i class="fas fa-microphone-alt-slash"> fa-microphone-alt-slash</i><br><i class="fas fa-music"> fa-music</i><br><i class="fas fa-volume-down"> fa-volume-down</i>     <i class="fas fa-volume-up"> fa-volume-up</i><br><i class="fas fa-volume-off"> fa-volume-off</i>         <i class="fas fa-volume-mute"> fa-volume-mute</i></p><h2 id="Styling"><a href="#Styling" class="headerlink" title="Styling"></a>Styling</h2><h3 id="Sizing-Icons"><a href="#Sizing-Icons" class="headerlink" title="Sizing Icons"></a>Sizing Icons</h3><h2 id="Other-Icon-Options"><a href="#Other-Icon-Options" class="headerlink" title="Other Icon Options"></a>Other Icon Options</h2><p>What if I want to use certain icons in my project, but I can not find a proper one from Font Awesome? What are the next step options available?</p><h2 id="Option2-iconfont"><a href="#Option2-iconfont" class="headerlink" title="Option2: iconfont"></a>Option2: iconfont</h2><h2 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h2><ul><li>Font Awesome.com: <a href="https://fontawesome.com/v5.15/how-to-use/on-the-web/referencing-icons/basic-use">Basic Use</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
